Philadelphia 76ers Beat Miami Heat 86-82 to Avoid Sweep in NBA Playoffs

-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 
2011-04-24T21:10:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-24/philadelphia-76ers-beat-miami-heat-86-82-to-avoid-sweep-in-nba-playoffs.html
The Philadelphia 76ers beat the
Miami Heat 86-82 to avoid a sweep in their National Basketball
Association first-round playoff series.  Trailing 3-1 in games in the best-of-seven Eastern
Conference series, the 76ers head back to Miami for Game 5 on
April 27.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  